cdata.name: ForexCoin
cdata.desc: Forexcoin is a Pow/PoS cryptocurrency developed by group of forex traders with experience in Forex trading, Stock Market and Crypto currency trading. FOREX traders will trade with the ICO funds in different markets and use the profits to develop the Forexcoin. The share holder and miner who has the ForexCoin will be getting 120% profit per annum.
